# Change Log

All notable changes to brdkREST will be documented in this file.
The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](http://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/)
and brdkREST adheres to [Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

## [1.2.0] - 2022-06-28
### Added
- brdkRESTImgGW.parameters - Able to add parameters to the client call to retrieve the image

### Fixed
- brdkRESTServer - Reponse buffer and length updated before response is sent

## [1.1.0] - 2022-05-31
### Added
- MIME PNG, GIF, JPG, BMP images
- HTTP status, 500, 501, 503
- brdkRESTImgGW - An image gateway. Gets an image from an URL and hosts a 64 based version of the image.

## [1.0.0] - 2022-04-18
### Added
- brdkRESTClient - REST client implementation
- brdkRESTServer - REST server implementation
- brdkRESTtoJSON - Add name and value pair to a JSON object. NB Function does NOT check if the string is large enough.
- brdkRESTfromJSON - Finds a name and value pair in a JSON object. $RETURN=length;Length of the string. -1 means name not found.
